Binary Analog WatchFace: A beautiful and clean Binary WatchFace

The inner ring show you the hour in 8bit binary format
The middle ring shows you the minutes
The outer ring shows you the current minute in seconds

Its a minimal and elegant watchface showing you the time in binary
